约翰·库珀·克拉克、尼什·库马尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/glastonbury-2024-theatre-and-circus.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/glastonbury-2024-theatre-and-circus-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/glastonbury-2024-theatre-and-circus-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/glastonbury-2024-theatre-and-circus-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/glastonbury-2024-theatre-and-circus-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/glastonbury-2024-theatre-and-circus-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>随着剧院和马戏团法案的公布，詹姆斯·阿卡斯特 (James Acaster)、约翰·库珀·克拉克 (John Cooper Clarke) 和尼什·库马尔 (Nish Kumar) 成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里</a>演出阵容中最新加入的名字。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 2024：查看迄今为止的完整阵容和舞台划分</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年的标志性节日将于 2024 年 6 月 26 日星期三至 6 月 30 日星期日在萨默塞特皮尔顿的沃西农场举行，届时将有大量马戏、戏剧、歌舞表演、音乐、舞蹈和诗歌表演。</p><p>早在三月份就有消息称，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队 (Coldplay)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-revealed-who-playing-poster-3600775">将在今年夏天的金字塔舞台 (Pyramid Stage) 上领衔主演</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain)</a>将在传奇舞台上表演。</p><p>剧院和马戏团区其他新宣布的表演和表演包括喜剧演员安迪·帕森斯、诗人艾奥娜·李、戏剧和舞蹈团马克·布鲁斯公司、音乐家托比·沃克、歌舞表演《没有凯特·布什的夜晚》、Boom Circus 等等。</p><p>您可以在下面查看完整的舞台阵容。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">距离大门开放仅剩 51 天，这是 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里令人难以置信的<a href="https://twitter.com/theatre_circus?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@theatre_circus</a>球场的阵容<a href="https://t.co/SmvPdkF146">pic.twitter.com/SmvPdkF146</a></p><p> - 格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 (@glastonbury) <a href="https://twitter.com/glastonbury/status/1787422185084096623?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 5 月 6 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>今年将在音乐节金字塔舞台上表演的其他乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">Burna Boy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pj-harvey">PJ Harvey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cyndi-lauper">Cyndi Lauper</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-kiwanuka">Michael Kiwanuka</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janelle-monae">Janelle Monae</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-dean">Olivia Dean</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paloma-faith">Paloma Faith</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keane">Keane</a> 。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">Idles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/disclosure">Disclosure</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a>计划在 Other Stage 上名列前茅，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-streets">The Streets</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/two-door-cinema-club">Two Door Cinema Club</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">Avril Lavigne</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a>等乐队将在整个节日期间进行表演。各个阶段。</p><p>最近公布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-announce-full-2024-line-up-for-west-holts-stage-3751305">2024 年 West Holts 舞台阵容的</a>许多其他新名字，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Nia-Archives">Nia Archives</a>和 47soul 以及之前宣布的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Jessie-Ware">Jessie Ware</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Justice">Justice</a> 。</p><p>最近几周，音乐节逐渐减少了多个舞台的阵容，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-adds-more-names-to-line-up-acoustic-stage-3616963">Acoustic Stage</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/caity-baser-lulu-frank-turner-and-skindred-among-new-names-for-glastonbury-2024-line-up-in-field-of-avalon-reveal-3618404">Field Of Avalon</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-shares-massive-shangri-la-area-line-up-for-2024-with-kneecap-bob-vylan-lambrini-girls-gorgon-city-and-more-3620049">Shangri-La 区</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-english-teacher-sprints-bob-vylan-and-lottery-winners-among-acts-for-left-field-line-up-3752348">Left Field</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-announce-stacked-line-up-for-woodsies-area-3752059">Woodsies</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-fatboy-slim-camelphat-groove-armada-lead-glastonbury-2024-glade-area-line-up-3749471">The Glade</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-romy-kelly-lee-owens-shygirl-and-more-added-to-glastonbury-as-silver-hayes-line-up-revealed-3751900">Silver Hayes</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-announces-2024-line-up-for-the-common-3753302">The Common</a> 。</p><p>在格拉斯顿伯里最近的其他新闻中， <em>NME</em>采访了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/JayaHadADream">JayaHadADream</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/JayaHadADream"> </a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-jayahadadream-emerging-talent-competition-winner-interview-radar-3751748">讲述在赢得 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节新兴人才竞赛后，今年夏天赢得令人垂涎的格拉斯顿伯里音乐节席位的感受</a>。</p><p> “这感觉完全超现实，也温暖人心、令人安心，”她谈到这一荣誉时说道。 “有这么多新兴艺术家在做着令人惊叹的事情，所以在如此繁忙的氛围中看到和听到这些都是令人难以置信的，特别是在女性代表性不足的嘻哈音乐中。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">请访问此处，了解 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的完整阵容</a>以及迄今为止的舞台划分。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-